"{\"uid\": \"santacruzsentinel.com-2024-08-10-aptos-native-nikki-hiltz-takes-seventh-in-1500-2024-summer-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"e-Edition  Sign up for email newsletters    Sign up for email newsletters  e-Edition  Trending:  American track and field talent Nikki Hiltz was intent on medaling at the 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 201, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 97, \"end\": 105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999998342873506, \"rank\": 1.4170162440723832e-07, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 129, \"end\": 140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nikki_Hiltz\", \"score\": 0.9999994965743456, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nikki Hiltz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nikki_Hiltz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nikki_Hiltz\"}, {\"begin\": 195, \"end\": 200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999968168, \"rank\": 3.19853589667297e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Aptos native fell short of that goal, but still produced an inspirational and historic showing.\", \"from\": 202, \"to\": 301, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 29-year-old, who identifies as transgender/nonbinary and uses they/them pronouns, became the first openly trans athlete to compete in an Olympic final in an individual event.\", \"from\": 303, \"to\": 481, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Aptos native placed seventh in the women's 1,500 final in 3 minutes, 56.38 seconds on Saturday, the penultimate day of the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 622, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To measure my Olympic experience off of less than a 4-minute race would be such a disservice to this whole journey,\\\" Hiltz said.\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 753, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have had such an incredible time and really taking it all in, walking away very happy.\\\"\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 844, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hiltz had plenty of reasons to be proud of their showing.\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 903, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They had just one sub-4 finish in the 1,500 prior to 2024 but continued to show their potential.\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 1000, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They have posted finishes of 3:56 or faster three times this year, including twice in the past three days.\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1107, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hiltz's parents made the trip from Aptos to the Stade de France in Saint-Denis, France, to cheer on their offspring.\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1144, \"end\": 1149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nordic_Naturals_Challenger\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.658329645569833e-15, \"text\": \"Aptos\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nordic_Naturals_Challenger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nordic_Naturals_Challenger\"}, {\"begin\": 1176, \"end\": 1187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 0.999999999362899, \"rank\": 3.9449408361511426e-10, \"text\": \"Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}, {\"begin\": 1189, \"end\": 1195, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9919573028533393, \"rank\": 0.006533673477871702, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That said, Hiltz, a former talent at University of Oregon and later University of Arkansas, has support groups around the world.\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1354, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hiltz an inspiration in the LGBTQ community.\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1399, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Millions of fans were glued to their televisions to take in the 1,500 final.\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1477, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some of them went to Zelda's on the Beach in Capitola Village for a watch party to support Hiltz.\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1575, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1499, \"end\": 1504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Legend_of_Zelda\", \"score\": 0.9837932589081027, \"rank\": 0.014575256676684792, \"text\": \"Zelda\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Legend_of_Zelda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Legend_of_Zelda\"}, {\"begin\": 1523, \"end\": 1531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Capitola,_California\", \"score\": 0.9967839191709859, \"rank\": 0.0032264569469659947, \"text\": \"Capitola\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Capitola,_California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Capitola,_California\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What those restaurant viewers witnessed, as did the rest of the world, was a historic showing from Kenyan 30-year-old Faith Kipyegon.\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1710, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1695, \"end\": 1709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Faith_Kipyegon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Faith Kipyegon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Faith_Kipyegon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Faith_Kipyegon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kipyegon ran the race of her life and claimed her third straight gold in an Olympic-record 3:51.29.\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1813, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She broke her own mark of 3:53.11, set at the Tokyo Games in 2021.\", \"from\": 1814, \"to\": 1880, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She is the first athlete - male or female - to win gold in the event at three different Games.\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1976, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a big, big achievement,\\\" Kipyegon said.\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 2023, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was really looking forward to defending my title (from the last two Olympic Games), and I had a dream.\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2129, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's amazing to me, I completed it.\", \"from\": 2130, \"to\": 2165, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am so, so happy.\", \"from\": 2166, \"to\": 2184, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is history.\", \"from\": 2186, \"to\": 2203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I managed to make history.\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2230, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have done it.\", \"from\": 2231, \"to\": 2246, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is an amazing honor, to win the gold medal in the 1,500.\", \"from\": 2247, \"to\": 2308, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was my key target.\\\"\", \"from\": 2309, \"to\": 2331, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Australia's Jessica Hull won silver in 3:52.56, and Great Britain's Georgia Bell earned bronze in a national record time of 3:52.61.\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2465, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2333, \"end\": 2342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.8518906155933578, \"rank\": 0.11546303664450472, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 2345, \"end\": 2357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Hull\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jessica Hull\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Hull\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Hull\"}, {\"begin\": 2385, \"end\": 2398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9985179141370206, \"rank\": 0.0014820790178336463, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2401, \"end\": 2408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Bulldogs\", \"score\": 0.9906261349428763, \"rank\": 0.004983334552997699, \"text\": \"Georgia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Bulldogs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Bulldogs\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's all a bit of a blur,\\\" Bell said.\", \"from\": 2467, \"to\": 2505, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think it'll hit me a little bit later.\", \"from\": 2506, \"to\": 2547, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On the start (line) I really had the feeling that if I just stuck in there, I'd be able to do something special, so I am over the moon to get a medal.\\\"\", \"from\": 2548, \"to\": 2699, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hiltz, possessing a big, warm smile, helped an exhausted runner up from the track after the race and congratulated several runners on their showing, including the medalists.\", \"from\": 2701, \"to\": 2874, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hiltz, who smashed the U.S. Olympic Trials record in a 3:55.33 finish last month in Oregon, took third place in both the first round and semifinals in France.\", \"from\": 2876, \"to\": 3034, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2904, \"end\": 2918, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_trials_(track_and_field)\", \"score\": 0.8581582794952675, \"rank\": 0.038961038961052005, \"text\": \"Olympic Trials\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_trials_(track_and_field)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_trials_(track_and_field)\"}, {\"begin\": 2960, \"end\": 2966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\", \"score\": 0.9983334236690736, \"rank\": 0.001451581850722528, \"text\": \"Oregon\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\"}, {\"begin\": 3027, \"end\": 3033, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9919573028533393, \"rank\": 0.006533673477871702, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their success has skyrocketed so high over the past two years that Hiltz envisioned medaling in her first Olympics appearance.\", \"from\": 3036, \"to\": 3162, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Why not me?\\\"\", \"from\": 3164, \"to\": 3177, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"said Hiltz, after the semifinals.\", \"from\": 3178, \"to\": 3211, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The stars did not align.\", \"from\": 3213, \"to\": 3237, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hiltz got boxed in early and drafted the lead pack for much of the first three laps.\", \"from\": 3238, \"to\": 3322, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hiltz got tangled up with another runner just before the bell sounding the final lap was rung.\", \"from\": 3323, \"to\": 3417, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They maintained their footing while breaking stride, but they were unable to have their infamous kick secure a podium finish.\", \"from\": 3418, \"to\": 3543, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Regardless of the outcome, Hiltz's fans will continue to support their racing hero.\", \"from\": 3545, \"to\": 3628, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact,several thousand of them have signed a petition to General Mills executives in an attempt to get Hiltz featured on their Wheaties cereal box.\", \"from\": 3630, \"to\": 3779, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3689, \"end\": 3702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_Mills\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"General Mills\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_Mills\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_Mills\"}, {\"begin\": 3759, \"end\": 3767, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wheaties\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wheaties\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wheaties\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wheaties\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's an honor typically reserved for champions, and, to them, Hiltz is a champion.\", \"from\": 3781, \"to\": 3863, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympics.com and Citiusmag.com contributed to this report.\", \"from\": 3865, \"to\": 3923, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3865, \"end\": 3877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999995989128, \"rank\": 4.009492999857878e-10, \"text\": \"Olympics.com\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Women's 1,500 meters  1.\", \"from\": 3925, \"to\": 3949, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Faith Kipyegon, Kenya, 3:51.29.\", \"from\": 3950, \"to\": 3981, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3950, \"end\": 3964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Faith_Kipyegon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Faith Kipyegon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http:/